---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="About VoiceROI - Eliminating the Human Handbrake™" description="Learn how VoiceROI's AI Digital Workers eliminate the Human Handbrake™ and help businesses capture every revenue opportunity 24/7.">
  <Header />
  
  <main class="pt-20">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="section-padding bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-white">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center animate-on-scroll">
          <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black text-black mb-6">
            Eliminating the
            <span class="text-lime-400">Human Handbrake™</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            VoiceROI was founded on a simple truth: every business is limited by human availability. We exist to break that limitation forever.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Mission Section -->
    <section class="section-padding bg-white">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div class="animate-on-scroll">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-black text-black mb-6">
              Our Mission
            </h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
              We believe every business owner deserves to operate at the speed of opportunity, not the speed of human limitations. The Human Handbrake™—those biological constraints that force your business to miss calls, delay responses, and lose revenue—doesn't have to define your growth ceiling.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
              Our AI Digital Workers eliminate this friction permanently, creating a business that captures every opportunity, operates 24/7, and scales without the traditional constraints of hiring, training, and managing human staff.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-lime-400 rounded-2xl p-6">
              <p class="text-black font-semibold text-lg">
                "We don't just provide technology—we deliver guaranteed results. Your success is our business model."
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="animate-on-scroll">
            <img 
              src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dil14r8je/image/upload/v1768292445/auto-site-builder/VoiceROI/image_0.png" 
              alt="VoiceROI Mission"
              class="w-full rounded-2xl shadow-2xl"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- The Problem Section -->
    <section class="section-padding bg-black text-white">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="text-center mb-16 animate-on-scroll">
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-black mb-6">
            The Human Handbrake™
            <span class="text-lime-400">Problem</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            Every business faces the same fundamental limitation
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
          <div class="animate-on-scroll text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-lime-400 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-black" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Limited Hours</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300">Business stops when humans stop working</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="animate-on-scroll text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-lime-400 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-black" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Missed Calls</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300">62% of business calls go unanswered</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="animate-on-scroll text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-lime-400 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-black" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Scaling Limits</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300">Growth requires expensive hiring and training</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="animate-on-scroll text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-lime-400 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-black" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v3m0 0v3m0-3h3m-3 0H9m12 0a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Inconsistency</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300">Human performance varies with mood, energy, and attention</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Our Solution Section -->
    <section class="section-padding bg-white">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="text-center mb-16 animate-on-scroll">
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-black text-black mb-6">
            Our
            <span class="text-lime-400">Solution</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            Results-as-a-Service™: We don't sell software, we guarantee outcomes
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="animate-on-scroll bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-lime-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <span class="text-2xl font-black text-black">AI</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black mb-4">Digital Workers</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              Custom-programmed AI agents that handle calls, qualify leads, book appointments, and follow up—perfectly, every time.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="animate-on-scroll bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-lime-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <span class="text-2xl font-black text-black">24/7</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black mb-4">Always Available</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              Your digital workforce operates around the clock, capturing opportunities while you sleep, vacation, or focus on growth.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="animate-on-scroll bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-lime-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <span class="text-2xl font-black text-black">ROI</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black mb-4">Guaranteed Results</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              We share the risk of your success. If we don't deliver measurable results in 6 months, we work for free until we do.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Values Section -->
    <section class="section-padding bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-white">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center mb-16 animate-on-scroll">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-black text-black mb-6">
              Our
              <span class="text-lime-400">Values</span>
            </h2>
          </div>
          
          <div class="space-y-12">
            <div class="animate-on-scroll flex items-start space-x-6">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-lime-400 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <span class="text-black font-bold text-lg">1</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black mb-3">Results Over Promises</h3>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                  We don't sell hope—we deliver guaranteed outcomes. Our Results-as-a-Service™ model means we only succeed when you do.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="animate-on-scroll flex items-start space-x-6">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-lime-400 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <span class="text-black font-bold text-lg">2</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black mb-3">Eliminate Friction</h3>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                  Every process, every interaction, every system we build is designed to remove the friction that limits your growth.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="animate-on-scroll flex items-start space-x-6">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-lime-400 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <span class="text-black font-bold text-lg">3</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black mb-3">Continuous Improvement</h3>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                  Our Meta Agent™ technology continuously optimizes your digital workforce, ensuring performance improves over time.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="section-padding bg-lime-400">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="text-center animate-on-scroll">
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-black mb-6">
            Ready to Eliminate Your Human Handbrake™?
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-black/80 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Join hundreds of businesses that have broken free from human limitations and achieved extraordinary growth.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a href="/demo" class="btn-secondary px-8 py-4 text-lg">
              Book Your Free Demo
            </a>
            <a href="/contact" class="text-black font-semibold hover:underline text-lg">
              Contact Our Team →
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>